  "texts": [
    "Deep learning can unlock the power of climate data by analyzing its low-resolution obtained from numerical models instead of regional high-resolution counterparts.",
    "The proposed approach tackles the challenges of the computational burden and information overload to obtained high-resolution regional data from weather numerical models.",
    "The integration between deep learning and numerical data can offer faster analysis, targeted feature extraction, uncovering",
    "The accuracy of both detectors decreased when tested on LR images.",
    "However, the proposed approach utilizing Faster R-CNN and SSD achieved 81.9% and 74.1% AP."
  ]
}